---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="ALG for Hiring - Advocacy-Led Growth"
  description="How HR and talent teams use ALG: employer branding, role amplification, hiring visibility through employee networks."
  activeNav="hiring"
>

  <div class="section animate-in">
    <div class="section-label"><span class="num">&rarr;</span> alg/hiring</div>
    <h1 class="t-heading-1" style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);">Hiring</h1>

    <p class="section-body mb-8">
      You're paying agencies 15-25% per hire to reach a talent pool your employees are already
      connected to. You've tried asking people to share job posts. It feels forced because it is.
      The employer brand lives in a careers page nobody visits.
    </p>

    <p class="section-body mb-8">
      Meanwhile, your new hires are excited. Your promoted employees are proud. Your teams just
      shipped something real. These moments - when sharing feels like expression, not obligation -
      are the hiring distribution channel nobody's activating.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-heading-2" style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-4); margin-top: var(--sp-10);">The Completion Moments for Hiring</h2>
    <div class="principles-list mb-8">
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="principle-dash">-</span>
        <p class="principle-text"><strong>Onboarding completion</strong> - new hire just finished their first week/month. Peak belief in the company. Natural share: "Just joined [company]. Here's why."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="principle-dash">-</span>
        <p class="principle-text"><strong>Promotion or milestone</strong> - career growth made visible. Natural share: "Promoted to [role] at [company]." Network sees a company that grows its people.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="principle-dash">-</span>
        <p class="principle-text"><strong>Team achievement</strong> - product launch, award, milestone. Cohort activation: multiple team members sharing simultaneously creates signal cluster.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="t-heading-2" style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-4); margin-top: var(--sp-10);">The Hiring Cost Avoidance</h2>
    <div class="notation-block">
      <div style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);">Agency fees: <strong>15-25%</strong> per hire</div>
      <div style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);">At $120K salary: <strong>$18K-$30K</strong> per placement</div>
      <div>If ALG shifts 20% of hires from agency to organic advocacy: <span class="notation-highlight">direct cost avoidance</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="pull-quote">
      "The best employer brand isn't what the company says about itself. It's what employees say without being asked."
    </div>
  </div>

</Base>
